      "source": [
        "\n",
        "## My Lane as an ML Task\n",
        "\n",
        "Task Type: Scoring (Regression)\n",
        "\n",
        "My chosen lane is Content Refresh Prioritization.\n",
        "\n",
        "The objective is to predict a refresh priority score for each content page. The score helps identify which pages should be updated first based on historical content and engagement signals."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "R5LJlaJt_HO4"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Target or Proxy\n",
        "\n",
        "Target Column:\n",
        "refresh_priority_score\n",
        "\n",
        "This target represents the priority of refreshing a content page. Pages with higher scores should be refreshed before pages with lower scores."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "zUrwG4wD_Kkn"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Success Metric\n",
        "\n",
        "I would evaluate this model using RMSE (Root Mean Squared Error).\n",
        "\n",
        "A lower RMSE indicates that the predicted refresh priority scores are close to the actual scores."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "KDZp6iW__OKf"
      }
    },
